    dc:description "Figures 1, 2. Belciana jeremyi sp. n. 1. Paratype, Thailand, Lampang,Chae Hom 9 May 2021, photo #12 by Pasi Sihvonen (FNHM); b. male genitalia (slide MJP 663); c. aedeagus (slide MJP 663); d. 8th abdominal segment (slide MJP 663). 2. Paratype, Thailand, Lampang, Chae Hom 23 May 2015, photo by Pekka Malinen (FNHM); b. female genitalia (slide MJP 1059)." ;
